---<Layout title="About | Salerno Trucking" description="Family-owned Salerno Trucking has delivered professional mixer truck capacity and concrete delivery services since 2009."><PageHero eyebrow="Our Story" title="Built on Relationships. Driven by Responsibility." text="Since 2009, Salerno Trucking has built its reputation by showing up professionally, communicating clearly, and treating every customer's success as our responsibility." image="/images/fleet/sunset-truck.webp"/><section class="section"><div class="container split"><div class="reveal"><p class="eyebrow">Who We Are</p><h2>A Family Business Built for Long-Term Partnerships</h2></div><div class="reveal"><p class="lead">We provide mixer truck capacity and concrete delivery services across the United States.</p><p>Our work supports ready-mix producers that need dependable equipment and operators, and placement contractors who need reliable delivery and clear communication.</p></div></div></section><section class="section muted"><div class="container"><div class="values">{[['Respect','For every partner, operator, customer, and jobsite.'],['Integrity','Honest communication and dependable follow-through.'],['Stewardship','Care for the equipment and relationships entrusted to us.'],['Responsibility','Ownership of our performance and its impact.']].map(v=><article class="reveal"><h3>{v[0]}</h3><p>{v[1]}</p></article>)}</div></div></section><section class="image-feature reverse"><div class="feature-image about-image"></div><div class="feature-copy reveal"><p class="eyebrow">Our Vision</p><h2>To Be the Industry's Most Trusted Capacity Partner</h2><p class="lead">Known nationwide for professional representation, clear communication, and dependable service.</p></div></section><section class="cta"><div class="container centered"><h2>Put Our Experience to Work.</h2><a class="btn light-btn" href="/partner-with-us">Partner With Us</a></div></section></Layout>